{"tid":261910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 自私精!]荷蘭醫生私自授精 兒女或遍全國","createTime":"2017-05-28T22:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T23:25:50.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f5017b975a3746cf5835a4f31fa43e116bda26d","tid":261910,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T22:23:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170528/s00014/1495907500242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170528%2Fs00014%2F1495907500242&d=6EYkUlC4fZClXY%2B%2FZB2rRRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=503fa065\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170528%2Fs00014%2F1495907500242&h=b4304423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170528/s00014/1495907500242</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】今年4月逝世的荷蘭人工受精專家卡巴特（Jan Karbaat，圖），被揭生前幾十年私下以自己的精子為數十名求醫的婦女受精。這些婦女原本根據自身要求選擇了精子捐贈者，但卡巴特卻以自己的精子做替代品。現時有最少19人相信是他的子女，其中3人更是在其生育醫療中心以外的機構受精，顯示問題可能遍及全國。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cda368fd6fc6d23f540be52d9ba5e7ee671427b","tid":261910,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T22:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a9d19d9cf79be8bcf0c8d676fe9cc9596a57dd","tid":261910,"uid":6213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T22:52:35.000Z","msg":"諗起最近個套銀河守護隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p